metadata.name: HARMONY
metadata.description:
Location: Paris, Tour Eiffel.
Year: 2022.

Back in April I was in Paris, walking around the Eiffel Tower for the first time in my life shocked about the size of this monument, when I suddenly got to the perfect spot, where all was in harmony.

1/1 photography piece of the Eiffel Tower from a perspective that you have never seen before.
